{"tid":142658,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"在公司最後的29日 黎傾下上司啲仆街野","createTime":"2017-03-04T03:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T01:08:47.000Z","uid":44738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f697b564c1a02146ed83e85b7f00a8fb1cccaa2","tid":142658,"uid":44738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:24:43.000Z","msg":"細佬係一間地產公司到做後勤 做左一年<br />\n真係頂唔順上司條大仆街 (歡迎問發生咩事 答到盡量答)<br />\n信已遞 但都要對住佢一個月<br />\n<br />\n琴日串到佢認一認<br />\n依家叫我調位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d1c7a8cd7d8098d16238ee32215cb6887c2901","tid":142658,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"發生咩事？"},{"pid":"808d991146d2738962b58346c256c7e5e12aa832","tid":142658,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"點串法先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9011459abd2652454099783ee0790cbb4daf688b","tid":142658,"uid":44738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發生咩事？</blockquote><br />\n真係好多 由上年五月績到依家<br />\n<br />\n主要係一個人面獸心既大話精<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你想知哂？"},{"pid":"76989234be5a2c732c9779885f89cbef95156ccb","tid":142658,"uid":74851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:12:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>發生咩事？</blockquote><br />\n真係好多 由上年五月績到依家<br />\n<br />\n主要係一個人面獸心既大話精<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你想知哂？</blockquote><br />\n磨牙"},{"pid":"224611193570fba8a1f7481bea3b629a63b51037","tid":142658,"uid":44738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點串法先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n琴日無日啦啦 叫我同另一個同事 (我同佢都係senior)<br />\n之後係到問我地之前係whatsapp send 出黎既野係咪唔洗做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我同事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地過一過黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我上次講啲人message係咪諗住唔理？唔洗處理？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我未做到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地諗住點夾？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我無諗住夾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 禁你地做自己野<br />\n<br />\n之後一講完我就執野走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走先哂 bye"},{"pid":"88a8aa00b334b8587e0923438b969072601f6b01","tid":142658,"uid":44738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:04:29.000Z","msg":"今日大家一句野都無講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條契弟係到請個啲樣 係同我入職一撚樣<br />\n好想同啲入職講 條友柒架"},{"pid":"137974255fffbb87a2676a5d9decdd81ea5da5a5","tid":142658,"uid":76886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:37:02.000Z","msg":"最仆街 最深刻係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4a2742b4857621dae4c1ada0f61b3054da53d4","tid":142658,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:22:33.000Z","msg":"你上司係CK?"},{"pid":"18cc8cc9116cf18f01aebdf5d140a26c48448c21","tid":142658,"uid":44738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最仆街 最深刻係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最深刻一定係有個女同事離職<br />\n而我上司佢女同事既關係一向都差 大家都知<br />\n但其實係上司啲做事方式on9在先<br />\n<br />\n(講小小背景:我任職個間公司唔係咩大公司，中小企既地產公司，但都有架構，有十個董事，我同董事啲關係幾好，因為週不時都會見到)<br />\n<br />\n然後，上司就同我地講，十個董事都唔撚like我個女同事，話一致決定炒左佢。<br />\n<br />\n事後，我覺得好怪，雖然個女同事性格係差，但真係好勤力，凌晨都send啲文件上group。所以我就問哂啲董事，其中無一個話要炒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都係因為呢件事，開始對我上司有意見，真係唔係好相信覺得要對一個無力反抗既同事踩低佢，抬高自己"},{"pid":"f95bcb7e2548419dbafd54824703af293b8d15a4","tid":142658,"uid":44738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你上司係CK?</blockquote><br />\n唔係 R字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d5cefe47e546f47850d2ec910d734a9ec621f5","tid":142658,"uid":44738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日大家一句野都無講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條契弟係到請<span style=\"color: red;\">人</span>個啲樣 係同我入職一撚樣<br />\n好想同啲入職講 條友柒架</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c75f594d554aa1a2025b1c71650f6bf3e5b40bc0","tid":142658,"uid":44738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1e09a50cf08509d1c46cb3c65a92e13b95bbdf","tid":142658,"uid":44738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:08:47.000Z","msg":"無見條仆街兩日 翻緊公司<br />\n原定今日交野比佢<br />\n唔知會唔會破冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}